data.description: Introducing a charming gem in the sought-after school district of Republic, Missouri. This beautiful three-bedroom, one-bathroom home with a one-car garage is ready to welcome its new owners. Situated in a quiet area, this property offers a serene setting with a fully fenced backyard, perfect for enjoying some peaceful outdoor moments.Step inside and be greeted by the numerous updates that make this home truly special. In September 2021, a new metal roof was installed, ensuring durability and providing added peace of mind for years to come. Showcasing timeless elegance and energy efficiency, new Anderson windows were installed in April 2021, allowing natural light to flood the interior. Enjoy the benefits of a new water softener, installed in September 2021, delivering purified water throughout the home. The kitchen boasts updated stainless steel appliances, bringing a touch of modernity to the heart of the home. Additionally, a new furnace and AC unit were installed in August 2020, ensuring comfort and efficiency year-round. This home offers a prime location with nearby amenities, including parks and shopping! Don't miss the chance to call this one Home Sweet Home! Call for your private showing today!
